  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WZDataEvent
    Represents a named event with an optional set of parameters that be sent and received during a broadcast streaming session.
    WZDataItem
    The primary class for representing stream metadata, the server connection query string, and WZDataEvent parameters
    WZDataList
    An array-like list of WZDataItem elements that can be used as a named parameter for a WZDataEvent
